<p>*The <a href="Grammy" title="Grammy" class="mw-redirect">Grammy</a> went to Johnny Lee and Tony Lane. The photo featured on the front cover of the album was expertly airbrushed to paint a Danskin top on what was a topless photo of Carly.</p>
